data.name: Desc.Text
data.value:
Booking management system is a system for any country with include a lot of cities ,, and each city include a lot of hotels ,, and each hotel have different details. first you should fill all information about all cities and hotels in the country.
each city have name , id (auto) , description , photo for the most places of the city , and number of hotels (auto calculated).
each hotel have name , id (auto) , price per night , and photo for the hotel , and id for the city .
after you fill all information for each cities and hotels you can start your work, you can make booking request so easily without going to the location .
booking request require ( number of rooms , number of nights , select hotel ) and the program will display the total cost then you confirm the request .
you can modify informations of cities or hotels so easily .
else , you can delete city or hotel or booking request . ............................
